    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059040/extras/a65b695db1ba7888f3169e2c816754b6.avif?t=1771841865\" width=666 height=94 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cat-Astrophy</strong> 是一款快节奏且充满挑战的太空动作类 Roguelite：其 <strong>星光光标</strong> 系统和进化模块迫使你在每次运行中调整构建和玩法风格，带来混乱的战斗和精准跳跃。游戏始终紧张刺激，既奖励即兴操作，也奖励技术精通。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059040/extras/a623766ce0d2feb6a6976114b8ade33e.avif?t=1771841865\" width=600 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次游戏，你将探索程序生成的行星，组合技能、选择路径并掌握跑酷与实时战斗机制。每次运行都是独一无二的：发现改变能力的模块、揭示隐藏的协同作用，并决定是冒险前进还是用星碎片巩固永久升级。死亡是永久性的：死亡意味着学习、重构并以新策略再次尝试。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059040/extras/1ed2b1f4fa2c35b8fe8821b94054cdf9.poster.avif?t=1771841865\" width=1170 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059040/extras/1ed2b1f4fa2c35b8fe8821b94054cdf9.webm?t=1771841865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059040/extras/1ed2b1f4fa2c35b8fe8821b94054cdf9.mp4?t=1771841865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>宇宙程序化探索：</strong> 每次运行探索不同的行星，房间、路线和秘密不断变化，迫使你实时调整决策。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>敏捷战略战斗：</strong> 使用 <i>星光光标</i> 指挥精准攻击，同时移动 Polo；动作流畅、紧凑且充满风险与回报。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>每次运行独特构建：</strong> 发现模块并重新配置技能，创造完全改变游戏风格的组合。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>永久进度：</strong> 收集星碎片解锁持久升级，在不同运行间开启新路线和战术选项。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>路径与决策影响：</strong> 选择探索哪些行星和追求哪些奖励，你的选择塑造冒险的节奏与难度。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>跑酷与精准：</strong> 致命跳跃与高难度平台段落，每场遭遇融合移动与战斗。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>宇宙像素艺术美学：</strong> 色彩鲜明的世界、外星生物及个性化环境强化游戏的紧张和疯狂氛围。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>神秘剧情：</strong> 揭开 Polo 被绑架的原因，以及导致猫灾难的力量；剧情衬托动作，不抢占玩法核心。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059040/extras/5b7fb72bcaf5038d435bd777668be619.avif?t=1771841865\" width=652 height=94 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cat-Astrophy 适合追求强烈挑战、可重复游玩和有分量决策的玩家。每一次死亡都能教你新东西：学习、调整构建并战胜曾经击败你的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敢恢复 Polo 的记忆并面对无情的宇宙吗？<strong>将 Cat-Astrophy 加入你的愿望单</strong>，当 Demo 可用时试玩，并加入我们的社区提供反馈和建议协同与调整。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059040/extras/6ed6680f7c6a5496e83d5f8bd2a89597.poster.avif?t=1771841865\" width=1170 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059040/extras/6ed6680f7c6a5496e83d5f8bd2a89597.webm?t=1771841865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059040/extras/6ed6680f7c6a5496e83d5f8bd2a89597.mp4?t=1771841865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
